This is an implementation of the strategy design pattern.
It might get further updates such as the calculation of area and perimeter but for now it just prints messages if those are called. 
It implements the strategy design pattern by using interfaces instead of overriding the methods in every shape.

to run it you need to have MAKE installed on you system and on either mac or linux. 
use Make build command to build and then run the executable using ./test command
run this these commands in the sources directory. you can also run a make clean to delete the additional 